ys such as CFHTLenS, and we anticipate that\nsimilar shear measurement calibration strategies to those used for optical\nsurveys may be used to good effect in the analysis of SKA radio interferometer\ndata.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 15 Mar 2016 17:51:32 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 11 Aug 2016 13:09:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-09-23"}
