 less scatter and usually\ngive relations that would over-produce local galaxy counts.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 15 Mar 2016 20:00:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 1 Nov 2016 18:15:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-12-07"}
