ng the experimental design of studies. Our data are also\nsupportive of the feasibility of reliably reconstructing complex neuronal\nconnectivity using existing techniques.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 15 Mar 2016 22:25:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-03-17"}
