uperiority of our proposed full-duplex\nWPCN compared to the half-duplex WPCN and reveal interesting insights about the\neffects of perfect as well as imperfect self-interference cancellation\ntechniques on the network performance.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 16 Mar 2016 14:52:25 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 13 Feb 2017 09:26:03 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 16 Feb 2019 08:33:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-02-19"}
