f that energy is transferred to the accelerated\nprotons, whereas the case corresponding to a source distance of 13 kpc requires\neither a higher value of the energy released in the explosion or a larger\nenergy fraction to accelerate protons.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 16 Mar 2016 15:06:51 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-04-13"}
