ey are also of\ninterest for more visionary applications, such as quantum information\ntechnologies, based on self-assembled quantum dots.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 16 Mar 2016 15:14:41 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-03"}
